{"body": "Since it is possible to have `config.assets.digest` set to false in production, `assets:precompile` should probably not hard-code it to true.\r\n\r\nInstead the filename should be set based on the value of `config.assets.digest`. Something like:\r\n\r\n    filename = target.join(config.assets.digest ? asset.digest_path : logical_path)\r\n\r\nAlthough the manifest needs to update too... I'll submit a pull request.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/1963278", "created_at": "2011-08-31T23:24:23Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/2768#issuecomment-1963278", "updated_at": "2011-08-31T23:24:23Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 2768, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spohlenz/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spohlenz/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spohlenz/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/spohlenz", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spohlenz/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/spohlenz", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spohlenz/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/43da0307752bf635c44c33dcdd962a2e?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fd397c2b2be2178fe6247bd50fc97cff2.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spohlenz/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spohlenz/received_events", "gravatar_id": "43da0307752bf635c44c33dcdd962a2e", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spohlenz/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "spohlenz", "type": "User", "id": 7600, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spohlenz/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5238406ebd3543c1510108a1"}, "id": 1963278, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/2768"}
